title: #92Noon! DRAFT DAYYY!
description: Montage and Corey Chavous kick off the show, followed by an hour of draft-related takes. Ben Leber in studio for most of the 10am hour, Twins pitcher & sneaky sports rube Jake Odorizzi at 11, calls, and Charch to finish a festive 92Noon!
